Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.51,Dial-CH,,0,400,0,,这都什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.12,0:01:19.90,Dial-CH,,500,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.09,0:01:23.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.79,0:02:58.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「血型小测试」
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,提问
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我的血型是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么要问我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我感觉你可能会好奇
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.38,0:03:13.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以你知道吗 我猜你肯定不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,从印象上来判断是O型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过她这表情 答案可能不走寻常路
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就是最不可能的A型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但也有可能是B
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,依我的经验来看 像我姐那种B血型人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是不会自己主动聊起血型话题的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.91,0:03:32.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因为会遭受不正当迫害
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,用血型判断他人性格的人 多半是狗屎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我先套点线索出来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是AB型来着
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,天才血型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,上钩了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪有人会说自己是天才啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我懂了 你是A型
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我是AB
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对啊 山田是这样的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们血型一样呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,啊 其实我撒谎了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我不是AB
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.76,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你是什么血型
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,别聊血型了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,知道了也没什么用
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,人的性格也不能简单地分成4种
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,感觉也只有日本人有这种迷信
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.24,0:04:17.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川是B型
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「暗之能力者」
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,让我妈给我买了偏大一点的运动衫
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,过不了多久就会长高的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也对 毕竟初中生嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妈 谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,很有暗之能力者的风范
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然后那个3分就进了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,超常发挥
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,运气球啦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,虽然那一球之后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,到终场哨声响起前 我都再没摸到过一次球
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,奇迹的小林子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,努力过就好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,只要奇迹一直发生 它就不再是奇迹了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你真的行吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.41,0:05:08.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我忘东西了 你们先走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你… 你干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还以为你这衣服是跟别人借的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,别这样 外人一看还以为你打劫呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你把手伸出来
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,暗中交易
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,万一被发现了 受处分的人是我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我不能收
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,反正是空的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「喜欢的发型」
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,男生最喜欢的女生发型
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是单马尾哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,萌子说的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也看人吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.64,0:06:43.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那市川喜欢什么样的发型呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不可否认 单马尾是很棒
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但双马尾也挺好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 波波头也好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可是普通的短发也难以割舍
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不行 越想越觉得什么发型都很好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,根本选不出来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,深思熟虑
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我觉得你什么发型都好看啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是 我没问什么发型好看
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,问的是你喜欢哪种
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「换教室」
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,唉 该走了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我有东西忘拿了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你这是啥都没拿啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.23,0:07:45.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我帮你拿着
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她这是什么情况
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么是你啊 田山
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在这里干嘛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,等朋友而已啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,朋… 朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,下节课在化学教室？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我们班也在那边上 一起过去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.34,0:08:07.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,糟了 这两个人加上山田再加上我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,空气中必将弥漫着尴尬
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老师先前叫我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,让我先去趟办公室来着
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么老是被老师骂呀
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,长点心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.05,0:08:23.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也是啊 换教室上课
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她肯定是不想让人知道 是和我一起去的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原来她是要和我一起去啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.85,0:08:34.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「僵尸过家家」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,如果我成了僵尸 你能对我下杀手吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 能吧…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.15,0:08:52.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好像是破坏了头部才能让僵尸死透吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那… 那如果
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我还维持着自我意识呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,剧情太老套了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这种时候但凡犹豫就会死
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还是早点杀了好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不能出去
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还是能说话的僵尸？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我能持枪吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,服了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.63,0:09:36.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怪了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我… 我得杀了她啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,必须赶紧动手
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.47,0:10:00.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎哟 开枪开得太晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.63,0:10:03.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田死了 我也不活了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.28,0:10:12.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你现在
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,在干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.05,0:10:15.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没在干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你猜
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你想想
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.07,0:10:34.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「和老姐购物」
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田要是穿上这种衣服 应该好看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,把你杀了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,选好了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田的话
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,贪吃牛排套餐 超大份薯条
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再来份草莓酱松饼
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,儿童套餐在这里哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.01,0:11:10.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,很痒的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,又没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你真坏
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.72,0:11:24.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,如果山田有了男朋友 她也会这样吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我看你一直盯着别人看
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,以为你也想模仿呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,把你杀了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「肉包子」
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,买哪个呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要披萨包
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那我也
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.86,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那我换成肉包
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就不和我吃一样的是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,买的时候啥也没想 现在才发觉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次自己买零食
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.09,0:12:12.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.07,0:12:14.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好什么
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.15,0:12:16.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不会有学校里的人经过吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,店员或者谁打小报告的可能性也…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀 没人会经过的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,暖暖的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.15,0:12:56.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.02,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还行
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,看 买不一样的就是有这种好处
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可能明天就去世了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「香味」
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,用完了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老姐的 反正用了也没人知道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我闻到了女人的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还真有
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一闻就能闻出来
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我太惨了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这气味应该已经散了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你有没有闻到一股香味
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她也闻到了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是很好吃的那种
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,造成奇怪的误会也不好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,还是老实告诉她吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.29,Dial-CH,,600,0,0,,因为我不小心用了我姐的洗发液…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.71,Dial-CH,,0,600,0,,这家人今晚吃的是咖喱呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这家人今晚吃的是咖喱呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,啊… 呃 我用了我姐的洗发液
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.97,0:14:23.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我闻闻
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不过今天上了体育课 有点闻不出来了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「偷懒」
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,大大大鸡鸡
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.87,Dial-CH,,600,0,0,,甩啊甩啊甩
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.87,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,这人好烦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.16,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,离老娘远点
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.10,Dial-CH2,,600,0,0,,冲破小内内
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拖不干净
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,没劲 好想回家啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,卫生让保洁员来搞不好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那要不然
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.09,Dial-CH2,,0,0,0,,夜晚仍坚挺
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.84,0:14:59.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,偷懒吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,够了 闭嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.20,Dial-CH2,,0,0,0,,干嘛干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你这是性骚扰了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这也算？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要是没人搞卫生 就只能一直脏着了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,行 干净了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,其他地方也不脏
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,收工吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,收工了 就不算偷懒了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拿她没辙
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但总之去个没人的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,别人在搞卫生 不能碍事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.86,0:15:56.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.04,0:16:00.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都几点睡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.37,0:16:05.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,平时
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.91,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,1点左右
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,坏孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.04,0:16:13.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,11点半
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这不都过了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.67,0:16:31.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「僵尸过家家2」
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.26,0:16:41.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在想如果你变成了僵尸 我能下杀手吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不知道 杀呗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我有不好的预感
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来试试吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,行吧行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你快开始啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我在演啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,经她这么一说 我这确实和平时也没区别
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.63,0:17:12.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但万一你真的变成僵尸了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要怎么分辨你变没变呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.71,0:17:18.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,比如闻闻气味
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,或者听听心跳
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,靠近了就太危险了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.32,0:17:26.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就看你能不能说出我的名字 怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.09,0:17:27.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.36,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有可能忘不了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我就下不了手了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「拜拜」
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.23,0:18:00.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,从我嘴里说出拜拜太恶心了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,恶心 别
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎么办 我该怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.07,0:18:23.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,回头
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,见
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,明天可是周六
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Twi-Yaba
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,「圣诞老人红靴子」
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,看起来圣诞节快到了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,四川
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,来 这个给你
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.78,0:20:32.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但反正给的是垃圾 心知肚明了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那玩意我好像能穿上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.02,0:20:38.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,试试
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,穿不上的吧 这很硬的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,都说了穿不上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,肯定塞不进去
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什么什么 这什么情况
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.55,0:20:50.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,这什么情况
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.32,0:20:54.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,快进去了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也是 人生就是什么都要尝试
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
